metadata.name: Nightmare Fuel #1
metadata.description: Nightmare Fuel by JeffJag is an AI Art creation of seriously scary images. These images were created to fuel your nightmares and feature sensitive images. Some have depictions of fictional violence. All are made using AI art tools so any similarities between this art project and people places or things from actual reality are purely coincidental. Nightmare Fuel is also an open ended collection with new Seasons of drops marked by yearly events such as Halloween, etc. Tokens show Season information in the metadata. Certain tokens including the first 10 feature stories crafted using my ideas mixed with AI text generation tools and also come with licensing rights to use the images, names, and stories featured in the token art and metadata.
